data.description: Good starter home, with 2 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, two car attached garage, large living area, open kitchen with tons of cabinets and counter space,.  All appliances including washer and dryer.  Screened in back porch, workshop, RV hookup, and outside storage.  Garage is wired and vented for an additional bedroom should new buyers need one!   Quite neighborhood, close to Wallace College, minutes from Dothan.
